casebody.data:
Michael LEASE, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-4741 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 23, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The record on appeal is still on file in this court and was reviewed in addressing petitioner's petition alleging ineffective assistance of appellate counsel.

Petitioner's petition alleging ineffective assistance of appellate counsel is denied.

SILBERMAN, KELLY, and BADALAMENTI, JJ., Concur.
